author: Associated Press
title: Wyoming-Boise State game to be televised on ESPN2
text:
LARAMIE, Wyo. -- Wyoming's game at Boise State next Saturday will be televised on ESPN2.
The Mountain West Conference contest is scheduled to kick off at 8:15 p.m.
Wyoming is coming off its first win of the season, a 28-21 home victory over Nevada.
Boise State lost on the road at Utah State by a score of 52-26.
